on healthcare companies wrap programs insurance and taftharley the firm manages clientfocused equity and fixed income portfolios it launches and manages equity fixed income and balanced mutual funds for its clients the firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the united states it typically makes its equity investments in value stocks of smallcap and mid the firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals it also provides its services to public subadvisory investment companies pension and profit sharing plans pooled investment vehicles charitable organizations corporations state or municipal government entities endowment foundation healthcare companies wrap programs insurance and taftharley the firm manages clientfocused equity and fixed income portfolios it launches and manages equity fixed income and balanced mutual funds for its clients the firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the united states it typically makes its equity investments in value stocks of smallcap and midcap companies the firm employs a fundamental analysis with a bottomup stock picking approach to create its equity portfolios it benchmarks the performance of its smallcap portfolio against the russell  value index smallmid cap portfolio against the russell  value index and midcap portfolio against the russell mid cap value index the firm employs a valueoriented approach for short term fixed income portfolios it was founded in  and is based in charlotte north carolina with additional offices in atlanta georgia burlingame california raleigh north carolina washington district of columbia and virginia beach virginia sterling capital management llc operates as a subsidiary of bbt corporation detailed description  congress streetsuite charlotte nc united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwsterlingcapitalcom key executives for sterling capital management llc mr alexander worth mcalister president senior md  member of the board of director mr j